{
  "stem": "26609.16",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they had to sign some documents how many people she brought in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And as I said before, she had about 30 people on her farm including me-- left me in a queue.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And she said, Wanda, like others, you go in there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "In the hospital, there was one room.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I think a laboratorium or what, pathology what it was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I liked always to be the last, like in prison, or like when we went in-- [PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] when we were sent to Germany.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I waited.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "One after one we went in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It took a little time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I haven't seen them coming back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So I thought there must be the other side a door.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Go in here, and get out on the other side.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Finally came to me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "When it came to me, she appeared and went in with me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] I think she had to give them my papers, whatever it was signed when she took me from that [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We went in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "There was a doctor behind a desk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] And he took, normally, as you take blood for a test from a finger.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They didn't need much blood-- not from the vein, but from top finger-- and put it into blotting paper.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "You know, you put it on blotting paper.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I looked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I wanted to see.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Even if I have to die here, I want to see what it is.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I looked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And I have seen as he took it, she looked at it too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And it was a very dark, nearly black spot of that blood on the blotting paper.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "She screamed out, Wanda, [GERMAN]!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Wanda, you have dark blood!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] And then I fainted.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
